'''''Killer Force''''', izwi kandi ku izina rya '''''The Diamond Mercenaries''''', ni filime ishimishije yo mu 1976 iyobowe na Val Guest ikinwamo na Telly Savalas, Peter Fonda na Christopher Lee . <ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20090116084706/http://ftvdb.bfi.org.uk/sift/title/61291 ''The Diamond Mercenaries (1975)''] </ref> Byari ubufatanye hagati ya Repubulika ya [[Irilande]], [[Ubusuwisi]] na [[Amerika]] kandi yafashwe amashusho  cyane muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo. Umugambi wayo ni agatsiko k'abagizi ba nabi bategura ubujura bukomeye mu kirombe cya diyama .

== Umugambi ==
Umuyobozi w’umutekano Harry Webb afite ubwoba ko ubujura bwa diyama bugiye kubera mu ruganda rukora ubucukuzi bw’amabuye y'agaciro mu butayu. Yahise abasha gukundwa cyane,  na Claire Chambers, umukobwa wamamaye cyane  n'umukobwa w'umuyobozi w'ibirombe. Arimo gusura umugabo akunda, Mike Bradley, ushinzwe umutekano kuri iki kirombe.

Nelson, umuyobozi w’ibirombe, aha Bradley ubutumwa bw'amatsiko - kwiba diyama. Arashaka kugira uruhare kuri Bradley kugira ngo amuhuze na Lewis runaka witegura kwiba ikirombe abifashijwemo n'itsinda ry'abacanshuro ndetse n'ibikoresho byaho bizwi nka Padiri Noheri. Webb, itamenyeshejwe uburiganya, idahwema gukurikirana Bradley, wavuganye na Lewis. Hamwe n'abacanshuro mugikorwa cyo kwinjira mu kirombe, Bradley yerekanye ko ari Padiri Noheri, wateguye iki gikorwa cyose. Hamwe na Webb ikurikirana, Bradley yahungiye mu butayu hamwe nabandi barokotse.

